51    /**
52    * A builder for FunctionTypes, because FunctionTypes are so
53    * ridiculously complex. All methods return {@code this} for ease of use.
54    *
55    * Right now, this mostly uses JSDocInfo to infer type information about
56    * functions. In the long term, developers should extend it to use other
57    * signals by overloading the various "inferXXX" methods. For example, we
58    * might want to use {@code goog.inherits} calls as a signal for inheritance, or
59    * {@code return} statements as a signal for return type.
60    *
61    * NOTE(nicksantos): Organizationally, this feels like it should be in Rhino.
62    * But it depends on some coding convention stuff that's really part
63    * of JSCompiler.
64    *
65    * @author nicksantos@google.com (Nick Santos)
66    * @author pascallouis@google.com (Pascal-Louis Perez)
67    */
